snippet.title: Dungeon Defenders II - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Dungeon Defenders 2 has been rebooted! Get ready for more tower defense, action, and loot soon! For more information check out this blog post from our new studio director, Dave Loyd:

http://dungeondefenders2.com/forum/showthread.php?104826-Dungeon-Defenders-II
